name: Polymer Clay "Black & Bud" Incense Holder
description:
This incense holder will keep your tables and shelves free of ash from your favorite standard sized incense. The holder is 5 inches wide and features an awesome border of bud leafs in three shades of green.

Cleans easily with soap and warm water. Comes with a free stick of incense!! Each piece is made by hand. A mold was not used in the creation process.
